gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 112, Bucks 97
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Bucks, 112-97. Paolo Banchero led the way for the Magic with 26 points, 12 rebounds and five assists, while Franz Wagner added 24 points, six rebounds and three assists in the victory. Giannis Antetokounmpo tallied 35 points, 10 rebounds and seven assists for the Bucks in the losing effort. The Magic improve to 5-4 on the season, while the Bucks fall to 5-4.
